<template lang="pug">
	.categories
		block-header
		block-content(:list="list ? list : []")
		block-footer
</template>

<script>
	import Header from '../blocks/includes/header.vue';
	import Footer from '../blocks/includes/footer.vue';

	import Content from '../blocks/categories/content.vue';
	import AOS from 'aos';

	import tempImageInclude1 from '../assets/img/_temp_cat-card1.png';
	import tempImageInclude2 from '../assets/img/_temp_cat-card2.png';
	import tempImageInclude3 from '../assets/img/_temp_cat-card3.png';

	export default {
		name: 'Categories',
		data: function(){
			return {
				list: [
					{
						label: 'Educational',
						bgImage: tempImageInclude1	,
						type: 'Educational'
					},
					{
						label: 'Entertainment2',
						bgImage: tempImageInclude2,
						type: 'Entertainment'
					},
					{
						label: 'Educational',
						bgImage: tempImageInclude3,
						type: 'Screen Recorder'
					},
					{
						label: 'Entertainment2',
						bgImage: tempImageInclude3,
						type: 'Entertainment'	
					},
					{
						label: 'Educational',
						bgImage: tempImageInclude2,
						type: 'Entertainment'
					},
					{
						label: 'Entertainment2',
						bgImage: tempImageInclude3,
						type: 'Entertainment'	
					},
					{
						label: 'Educational',
						bgImage: tempImageInclude1,
						type: 'Screen Recorder'
					},
					{
						label: 'Entertainment2',
						img: tempImageInclude2,
						type: 'Educational'	
					},
					{
						label: 'Educational',
						img: tempImageInclude2,
						type: 'Entertainment2'	
					},
				]
			}
		},
		components:{
			'block-header': Header,
			'block-footer': Footer,
			'block-content': Content
		},
		mounted() {
			this.$nextTick(function() {
				AOS.init({
					once: true,
					disabled: 'mobile',
					// offset: 0,
					duration: 1000
				});
			});
		}
	}

</script>

<style lang="scss">
	@import '@/assets/sass/ui.scss';
	@import '@/helpers/sass/aos.scss';
</style>
